* {{audio|en|en-us-declaration.ogg|Audio (US)}}
* {{audio|en|en-au-declaration.ogg|Audio (AU)}}
* {{rhymes|en|eɪʃən|s=4}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun|~}}

# A written or [[oral]] [[indication]] of a fact, opinion, intention, belief, etc.
#: {{ux|en|a '''declaration''' of love}}
# A list of items for various [[legal]] purposes, e.g. ''customs declaration.''
# The act or process of [[declare|declaring]].
# {{lb|en|cricket}} The act, by the [[captain]] of a batting side, of declaring an [[innings]] closed.
# {{lb|en|legal}} In [[common law]], the formal document specifying [[plaintiff]]'s [[cause of action]], including the facts necessary to sustain a proper cause of action, and to advise the [[defendant]] of the [[grounds]] upon which he is being [[sued]].
# {{lb|en|computing}} The specification of an object, such as a [[variable]] or [[function]], establishing its [[existence]] but not necessarily describing its contents.

